      "span_id": "p066_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0002",
      "text": " 47",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0003",
      "text": "4.2.18.4  RSCN initiative",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        209.26,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0004",
      "text": "An affected Nx_Port shall issue one RSCN Request for all state changes that occur prior to the initia-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        539.97,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0005",
      "text": "tion of the RSCN Request; multiple RSCN Requests shall not be queued for initiation.  An RSCN Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        540.01,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0006",
      "text": "quest shall be considered initiated when the SOF of the first frame of the RSCN Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.9,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0007",
      "text": "has been transmitted.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        192.02,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0008",
      "text": "4.2.18.5  RSCN registration",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        223.7,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0009",
      "text": "A node (Fabric Controller, service, Nx_Port) shall only issue RSCN requests to Nx_Ports that have",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        539.8,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0010",
      "text": "registered with the node to be notified of state changes.  These registrations shall be performed using",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        539.97,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0011",
      "text": "the State Change Registration (SCR) ELS.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        284.89,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0012",
      "text": "4.2.18.6  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        178.22,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0013",
      "text": "a) RSCN Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        238.96,
        238.42,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0014",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        262.96,
        287.89,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0015",
      "text": "4.2.18.7  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        227.07,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0016",
      "text": "Addressing: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        157.1,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0017",
      "text": "If the Fabric is using RSCN to notify a registered Nx_Port of a state change (see",
      "bbox": [
        157.08,
        310.96,
        539.68,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0018",
      "text": "4.2.18.2), the S_ID is the Fabric Controller, (FFFFFDh) and the D_ID is the address of the registered",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        539.93,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0019",
      "text": "Nx_Port destination.  If an affected Nx_Port is using RSCN to notify the Fabric or a registered",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        539.88,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0020",
      "text": "Nx_Port of a state change (see 4.2.18.3), the S_ID designates either the Nx_Port indicating a state",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        539.91,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0021",
      "text": "change to the Fabric Controller or the registered Nx_Port  and the D_ID is either the Fabric Control-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        540.03,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0022",
      "text": "ler, (FFFFFDh) or the address of the registered Nx_Port destination.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        397.08,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0023",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        140.41,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0024",
      "text": "The format of the RSCN Request Payload is shown in table 34.",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        394.96,
        419.75,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0025",
      "text": "The RSCN Payload fields are defined as follows:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        311.63,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0026",
      "text": "a)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        574.96,
        114.92,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0027",
      "text": " Page Length:",
      "bbox": [
        114.92,
        574.96,
        185.96,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0028",
      "text": " This field is the length in bytes of an affected Port_ID page.  This value is fixed",
      "bbox": [
        186.0,
        574.96,
        540.05,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p066_s0029",
      "text": "at 04h.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        586.96,
        152.93,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
